description: An established list of all possible alphanumeric codes and the desciptions. It is sometimes published and available online, but not always.
A list of all possible alphanumeric codes and the descriptions
A range of either numbers or letters (i.e. 1-25 or A-Z)
Attribute field used to join data tables with spatial feature classes (i.e. observational sensor data like rain, water level, atmospheric aerosols, etc.)
Free text entered by the creator of the dataset (i.e. - a title or dept name). There is no established set of codes.
